data.description: Stunning move in ready upgrades galore 3-bedroom 2 bath home located in north Crestview providing easy commute to the local bases, beaches, and shopping centers. Kitchen boats ample counter and cabinet space to meet all your cooking needs along with stainless steel appliances. The floor plan allows for a formal sitting area/dining area as well as the option to have a massive dining/living area in the den making it the ideal area of the home for friends and family to gather. Need more space, no problem, step back into the rear of the home for yet another great area for playroom, office, and whatever else you may need it for. This area has its very own mini unit to keep you comfortable throughout the year. All the bathrooms have been updated with stunning tile work including a spacious walk in shower in the master bath. Huge fenced in backyard provide plenty of play space for the kids and family dog to run around and play. There is also a storage/workshop building great for storage and perfecting your hobbies. There is a whole house generac generator as well providing you a peace of mind that the light will always remain on. Several local schools within walking distance or less than 3 minute drive away.   HVAC/Tankless Water heater-2019. Roof is 2023. Current insurance premium is around $2,300. Fireplace is not functional due to being capped off.  Schedule your showing today!!!
